We seek an experienced&nbsp;Senior Counsel with 8 or more years of civil litigation experience to join our team of award-winning litigators in the San Francisco Area. Tyson &amp; Mendes also offers attorneys the option to work for teams located in areas other than where they live. &nbsp;If you are licensed to practice in one of our states even if you do not live close to one of our offices, please let us know!


